Use the standard library
This is how to popcount of n:
   Remember that count is 0
   Remember that x is n
   Do this 1000 times:
      When x is 0, then:
         Leave the loop
      End when
      When remainder of x and 2 is 1, then:
         Increase count
      End when
      Remember that x is quotient of x and 2
   End do
   The answer is count
Now you know
>>> popcount of 0 
0
>>> popcount of 1 
1
>>> popcount of 2 
1
>>> popcount of 3 
2
>>> popcount of 7 
3
>>> popcount of 8 
1
>>> popcount of 255 
8
>>> popcount of 256 
1
>>> popcount of 1023 
10